The paper proposes a novel approach to sales forecast using Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) and structured data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper deals with forecasting, which is a common task in Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of historical sales data, which suggests that it may belong to the Database (cs.DB) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with optimizing the supply chain of manufacturers, which suggests that it may belong to the Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE) sub-category.
